comments: Migration_PMP_37:Plan validity will be extended by 180 days.Note-subscribers of withdrawn Per Minute/Per Second/ Lifetime/Student Special/General plans can also extend their validity using this voucher -- Free data 50MB to be consumed within 30 days

60 min any net voice call for 30 days reduced call rate to 03 BSNL and 02 non BSNL local numbers:onnet at 20per min offnet at 40p per min and reduced SMS charges for all(including F and F numbers):-local SMS at 10p per SMS and STD SMS at 50p per SMS.Subscriber can change F and F numbers with a charge of Rs5 per change per number.STV benefit is avilable in home LSA only.
